               <head>Saʻdi's Gulistan, with Bustan in margins</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>Saʻdī's didactic works, the Gulistān and Būstan. Although the quality of the manuscript is fine, it has suffered much from water damage, the decay of its fabric, and maltreatment. Not dated. The poor condition of the binding has revealed a number of legal and trade documents that may be worth studying in their own right. With owner's seals and inscriptions.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="IO_Islamic_4063-item1" class=" http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85100087">
                     <locus from="1v" to="162r">ff. 1v-162r</locus>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="n79139394">Saʿdī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="n79139394">سعدى</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Gulistān</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa">گلستان‏</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Transcribed in main text panel</p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="" xml:lang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="IO_Islamic_4063-item2"
                          class=" http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2002005579">
                     <locus from="1v" to="148v">ff. 1v-148v margins</locus>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="n79139394">Saʿdī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="n79139394">سعدى</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Būstān</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa">بوستان</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Transcribed in narrow column in margin</p>
                     </note>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
                  <objectDesc form="codex">
                     <supportDesc material="chart">
                        <support>Burnished cream paper cover in finely sprinkled flecks of gold within main text panel</support>
                        <extent>171 ff.<dimensions type="leaf" unit="mm">
                              <height>221</height>
                              <width>155</width>
                           </dimensions>
                           <dimensions type="written" unit="mm">
                              <height>147</height>
